    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Hard, shiny, tear-shaped seeds of a tropical grass; the seeds are sometimes used for jewelry or rosaries. The seed kernel is edible, and varieties are used as food product in parts of East Asia and in the Philippines.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
